{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ActionGroup"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Actions can be used to expose functionality in a structured way, either","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"from one part of a program to another, or to the outside world. Action"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"groups are often used together with a [type"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModel","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"] that provides additional"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"representation data for displaying the actions to the user, e.g. in a menu."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The main way to interact with the actions in a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GActionGroup"},{"type":"text","text":" is to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"activate them with [method","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.ActionGroup.activate_action"},{"type":"text","text":"]. Activating an"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"action may require a [type[Variant](\/\/documentation\/glib\/variant] parameter. The required type of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"parameter can be inquired with [method","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.ActionGroup.get_action_parameter_type","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Actions may be disabled, see [method","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.ActionGroup.get_action_enabled"},{"type":"text","text":"]."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Activating a disabled action has no effect.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Actions may optionally have a state in the form of a [type[Variant](\/\/documentation\/glib\/variant]. The current","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"state of an action can be inquired with [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.ActionGroup.get_action_state"},{"text":"].","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Activating a stateful action may change its state, but it is also possible to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"set the state by calling [method","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.ActionGroup.change_action_state","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"As typical example, consider a text editing application which has an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"option to change the current font to ‘bold’. A good way to represent"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this would be a stateful action, with a boolean state. Activating the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"action would toggle the state.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Each action in the group has a unique name (which is a string).  All"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"method calls, except [method","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.ActionGroup.list_actions"},{"type":"text","text":"] take the name of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"an action as an argument."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"code":"GActionGroup","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" API is meant to be the ‘public’ API to the action"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"group. The calls here are exactly the interaction that ‘external","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"forces’ (eg: UI, incoming D-Bus messages, etc.) are supposed to have","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"with actions. ‘Internal’ APIs (ie: ones meant only to be accessed by","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the action group implementation) are found on subclasses. This is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"why you will find – for example – [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.ActionGroup.get_action_enabled"},{"text":"]","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"but not an equivalent ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"set_action_enabled()"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Signals are emitted on the action group in response to state changes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"on individual actions."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Implementations of "},{"code":"GActionGroup","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" should provide implementations for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the virtual functions [method"},{"code":"Gio.ActionGroup.list_actions","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"] and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"code":"Gio.ActionGroup.query_action","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]. The other virtual functions should"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"not be implemented — their ‘wrappers’ are actually implemented with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"calls to [method","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.ActionGroup.query_action"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroup","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" type acts as an owner of an underlying "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GActionGroup"},{"text":" instance.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"It provides the methods that can operate on this data type through ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroupProtocol","isActive":true},{"text":" conformance.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroup","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" as a strong reference or owner of a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GActionGroup"},{"type":"text","text":" instance."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroupRef","type":"reference"},{"text":" (instead of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroup","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":") for a lightweight Swift reference to an underlying ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GActionGroup"},{"text":" instance.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroup","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO"]]},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"abstract":[{"code":"GActionGroup","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" represents a group of actions."}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"ActionGroup","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"ActionGroup","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"class","externalID":"s:3GIO11ActionGroupC","roleHeading":"Class","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ActionGroup","kind":"identifier"}]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/actiongroup"]}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroup\/init(_:)-35rnb","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroup\/init(_:)-5wayj","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroup\/init(_:)-6blu9","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\